@baseUrl = http://localhost:3003/api/v1

### 1. Upload Excel (saved to storage/uploads/mtn/)
POST {{baseUrl}}/mtn/subscriptions/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=----FormBoundary

------FormBoundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="msisdns.xlsx"
Content-Type: application/vnd.openxmlformats-officedocument.spreadsheetml.sheet

< ./msisdns.xlsx
------FormBoundary--

### 2. Start subscription for batch (calls MTN API in background)
POST {{baseUrl}}/mtn/subscriptions/batches/1/subscribe

### 3. List batches
GET {{baseUrl}}/mtn/subscriptions/batches

### 4. Batch status + queue summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/mtn/subscriptions/batches/1

### 5. Download stored Excel file
GET {{baseUrl}}/mtn/subscriptions/batches/1/file

### 6. Queue stats
GET {{baseUrl}}/mtn/subscriptions/queue/stats

### 7. Manually process one queue chunk
POST {{baseUrl}}/mtn/subscriptions/queue/process
